---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import TopNav from "../components/TopNav.astro";
---

<Base title="About — Full Bleed">
  <TopNav />

  <main class="about">
    <h1>For creatives, by creatives.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Full Bleed is a curated catalog of groundbreaking real-world AI work — the campaigns, workflows,
      and business plays that working designers, art directors, and photographers are actually shipping.
      Every entry shows the work, names the maker, and explains the how.
    </p>

    <h2 class="meta">How curation works</h2>
    <p>
      A pipeline watches maker communities around the web and surfaces candidates; an editorial pass
      kills most of them. What survives is real work, shown, with a workflow you could learn from.
      If a niche has nothing good, we publish nothing — empty-but-honest beats filler.
    </p>

    <h2 class="meta">Credit</h2>
    <p>
      Every entry credits its creator by name, links to the original post, and summarizes the work in
      our own words. We store only a small preview image; the work belongs to the people who made it.
      Featured and want something corrected — or just want it gone?
    </p>

    <h2 class="meta">Takedown</h2>
    <p>
      If you're the creator of featured work and want it removed or corrected, contact us and it
      happens — no questions, no friction. <span class="placeholder">[contact route lands with launch]</span>
    </p>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--s12) var(--s6) var(--s16);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: var(--w-display);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: var(--s4) 0 0;
  }

  h2.meta {
    color: var(--ink-35);
    margin: var(--s12) 0 var(--s2);
    padding-top: var(--s6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    font-weight: var(--w-med);
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-70);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .placeholder {
    color: var(--ink-35);
  }
</style>
